  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-02 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Multiple credibility factors report achieved levels substantially below required levels; nevertheless the decision record records an Accepted outcome, constituting a rebutting defeater (W-AR-02).",
